cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with improving word embeddings and word similarity using supervised learning techniques. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves training a Siamese Network to learn word similarity and reconstruct word embeddings. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves training neural networks, and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as word embeddings are often used in natural language processing tasks related to computer vision.
